    <text>
        <body>
            <div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1913-05-05T23:59:59-05:00"
                frus:doc-dateTime-min="1913-05-05T00:00:00-05:00" n="644"
                subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d644">
                <note rend="inline" type="source">File No. 888.001 Au 4/7.</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">The <gloss type="from">President of Haiti</gloss> to the
                            <gloss type="to">President</gloss>.</hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <seg rendition="#center">[Telegram.]</seg>
                </opener>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Port au Prince</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1913-05-05">
                            <hi rend="italic">May 5, 1913</hi>
                        </date>.</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>I thank you as well as the people of the United States and beg you to thank Mrs.
                    Wilson in behalf of Mrs. Tancredé Auguste for your condolences. The country is
                    very thankful for your high mark of sympathy.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Michel Oreste</hi>.</signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
